费送房的消息，方晴便是想要免费送房的业主之一。 她告诉记者，她要送掉的房子在广东省肇庆市四会市，目前房子还在，有几个人来咨询过，如果有人有意向接手，她可以配合去做合同公证。 不过，记者在采访中获悉，这些打着免费送房旗号的房源普遍存在高息贷款。所谓的免费送房，实际上是原业主希望有人能够承担剩余的贷款，而这些房子暂由于各种原因不能实际居住或出租，或业主方不能再负担每月高额的贷款，急于将资产脱手。 这种「免费送的房子」可以接手吗？不用付首付是否真的意味着捡了个大便宜？「本人房子免费送，已经供了 5 年」，「免费送房」再现，有人首付亏没了，业内人士提醒… | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f319a324ab1d159de36ae88ffda682f7_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "116 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/642842817"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIt4PF3vG0s7BWEAMaCTEwNTEzMTYzOSDK9futBjAAOMcHQAJyCTY0Mjg0MjgxN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1707093458.606100", "card_id": "Q_392618739", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 80}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "存不存在可以生吃，却不能做熟食用的食物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "存不存在生吃反而没事，一但做熟后（经过高温烹调后）就有毒（人吃了会中毒）的食物？ 如果真的存在这种食物，那它为什么会不存在？是基于什么化学原理或生物学原理吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f3a2d6c076560b48da3084b3714c5d5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "114 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/392618739"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It4PF3vG0s7BWEAMaCDQ5NTI3MTY3INy3wPUFMAA4uwFAA3IJMzkyNjE4NzM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1707093458.606809", "card_id": "Q_641179452", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010b